-- Minister Finley Says Canada Must Change Old Age Security Pension Plan
-- B y   L i e z e l   H i l l
-- 2012-02-21T18:25:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-21/minister-finley-says-canada-must-change-old-age-security-pension-plan.html
Demographics require the Canadian
government to make changes to the Old Age Security pension plan,
Human Resources Minister Diane Finley said today.  In a speech in Toronto, Finley said Canada will give
details of proposed changes to its public pension system in its
next budget, which is traditionally presented before the end of
March.  To contact the reporter on this story:
